# LXC 117 testbed network config.
# eth0 is demoted to manual. mwan-ifmgr owns DHCPv4 and SLAAC monitoring.
# IPv6 SLAAC is still kernel managed via accept_ra=2 because ifmgr only
# monitors v6, it does not assign addresses.

auto lo
iface lo inet loopback

auto eth0
iface eth0 inet manual
iface eth0 inet6 manual
